 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="robot-card"&gt;
 &lt;div class="robot-header"&gt;
 &lt;h2&gt;RAY&lt;/h2&gt;
 &lt;p class="robot-subtitle"&gt;Robot for Aquatic Yield&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="robot-body"&gt;
 &lt;div class="robot-img"&gt;
 &lt;img src="https://stxguy.github.io/images/robots/RAY.jpg" alt="RAY"&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="robot-info"&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;RAY is our robot that operates underwater. The purpose of the RAY is to study fish school dynamics and the interaction between robots and aquatic animals.&lt;/p&gt;
